44
00:02:53,400 --> 00:02:54,260
Sooner or later

45
00:02:54,360 --> 00:02:56,280
you'll regret this one day.

46
00:02:56,440 --> 00:02:58,840
Whether I'll regret it or not, I don't know,

47
