you've all been punished,

87
00:04:29,840 --> 00:04:31,500
you should learn your lesson.

88
00:04:36,360 --> 00:04:37,159
Zhiyi.

89
00:04:38,440 --> 00:04:39,400
Today,

90
00:04:39,840 --> 00:04:42,120
