personal relationships.

93
00:04:46,000 --> 00:04:47,460
This is your good fortune.

94
00:04:48,320 --> 00:04:49,600
I'm happy for you.

95
00:04:51,560 --> 00:04:53,800
But this opera profession

96
00:04:54,159 --> 00:04:56,680
is far more complex than you imagine.

97
00:04:58,080 --> 00:04:59,480
Even your senior brother

98
