101
00:05:10,840 --> 00:05:11,680
Dismissed.

102
00:05:14,040 --> 00:05:14,840
You

103
00:05:15,120 --> 00:05:16,560
little bastards.

104
00:05:19,640 --> 00:05:20,440
Junior.

105
00:05:22,520 --> 00:05:23,320
Senior.

