117
00:06:00,160 --> 00:06:02,040
If he hadn't suddenly appeared backstage,

118
00:06:02,040 --> 00:06:04,840
I would have definitely made it on stage this time.

119
00:06:06,640 --> 00:06:08,520
Most importantly,

120
00:06:10,520 --> 00:06:14,180
I even caused my senior to kneel down and beg for mercy on my behalf.

121
00:06:14,200 --> 00:06:15,680
He's the lead actor!

122
00:06:19,000 --> 00:06:21,440
You're still afraid of those rules, aren't you?

123
00:06:21,440 --> 00:06:22,560
I think in the future,

124
00:06:22,560 --> 00:06:25,560
you should just stop thinking about getting on stage.

125
00:06:27,600 --> 00:06:28,400
You know,

126
00:06:29,200 --> 00:06:30,240
that damn Feng Cun,

127
00:06:30,240 --> 00:06:31,900
what's he got to be so proud of?

128
00:06:32,120 --> 00:06:33,600
Can he paint facial patterns?

129
00:06:33,600 --> 00:06:35,080
Can he carry props?

130
00:06:35,120 --> 00:06:37,080
Can he even perform opera? He...

131
00:06:39,360 --> 00:06:41,760
But honestly, your skills still need work.

132
00:06:42,880 --> 00:06:44,880
You've snuck on stage so many times,

133
00:06:45,159 --> 00:06:47,240
but I've never seen you perform with Nanfeng.

134
00:06:47,240 --> 00:06:48,770
What roles have you played?

135
00:06:49,040 --> 00:06:50,120
Maids,

136
00:06:50,640 --> 00:06:51,720
soldiers...

137
00:06:51,920 --> 00:06:53,600
How dare you look down on me!

138
00:06:53,600 --> 00:06:55,600
You'll regret underestimating me.

139
00:07:01,880 --> 00:07:03,320
You really can't do anything,

140
00:07:03,320 --> 00:07:05,320
and you won't even let people say it.

141
00:07:06,880 --> 00:07:09,440
Just watch me carefully.

142
00:07:11,080 --> 00:07:12,240
I'm waiting.

143
00:08:42,799 --> 00:08:43,720
Well,

144
00:08:44,800 --> 00:08:46,460
that was actually quite good.

145
00:08:48,800 --> 00:08:50,840
See what happens when you underestimate me?

146
00:08:50,840 --> 00:08:52,440
Now you know.

147
00:08:57,520 --> 00:08:58,760
I'm impressed.

148
00:09:01,080 --> 00:09:04,010
It seems those people have eyes but can't see talent,

149
00:09:04,440 --> 00:09:07,500
unlike me, Master Ruan, who has the fortune to hear you.

150
00:09:08,760 --> 00:09:09,890
Stop joking around.

151
00:09:10,440 --> 00:09:12,760
I know you're just trying to comfort me.

152
00:09:15,360 --> 00:09:16,400
Tell me,

153
00:09:16,760 --> 00:09:18,880
