154
00:09:18,880 --> 00:09:21,240
on stage with my senior?

155
00:09:22,160 --> 00:09:25,000
I have such a small wish,

156
00:09:25,000 --> 00:09:27,480
why is it so hard to achieve?

157
00:09:29,080 --> 00:09:31,640
Master says I have good aptitude,

158
00:09:32,520 --> 00:09:35,200
it's just a pity I'm a girl.

159
00:09:36,400 --> 00:09:37,720
What's wrong with being a girl?

160
00:09:37,720 --> 00:09:39,240
Are you crazy?

161
00:09:42,640 --> 00:09:45,240
What I mean is that girls should sing when they deserve to.

162
00:09:45,240 --> 00:09:46,640
The audience isn't deaf.

163
00:09:46,760 --> 00:09:49,360
They can tell for themselves what sounds good.

164
00:09:51,040 --> 00:09:52,040
If all else fails,

165
00:09:52,680 --> 00:09:53,920
I'll build an entire theater

166
00:09:53,920 --> 00:09:55,000
just for you.

167
00:09:57,640 --> 00:09:58,640
Promise?

168
00:09:58,960 --> 00:10:00,760
You build the stage,

169
00:10:00,760 --> 00:10:02,240
I'll perform the opera.

170
00:10:04,400 --> 00:10:05,400
It's a deal.

171
00:10:35,880 --> 00:10:38,720
I hope that day really comes.

172
00:10:41,160 --> 00:10:42,920
If Huaiqing could see it,

173
00:10:43,760 --> 00:10:45,220
that would be even better.

174
00:10:47,600 --> 00:10:48,400
Who's Qing?

175
00:10:52,320 --> 00:10:54,600
He's my neighbor's younger brother.

176
00:10:56,680 --> 00:10:59,410
Our families have been friends for generations.

177
00:11:00,280 --> 00:11:02,240
We grew up together.

178
00:11:03,600 --> 00:11:05,000
But then,

179
00:11:05,800 --> 00:11:07,460
foreigners invaded the city,

180
00:11:07,960 --> 00:11:10,400
and our parents were killed.

181
00:11:12,440 --> 00:11:16,000
We had to make a living together.

182
00:11:18,480 --> 00:11:19,480
But...

183
00:11:21,600 --> 00:11:24,120
I lost him later.

184
00:11:28,160 --> 00:11:30,290
If it weren't for my master and senior,

185
00:11:31,560 --> 00:11:32,440
I probably

186
00:11:33,120 --> 00:11:34,440
wouldn't be able

187
00:11:34,440 --> 00:11:36,320
to sit here drinking with you now.

188
00:11:39,520 --> 00:11:40,440
So,

189
00:11:41,560 --> 00:11:42,520
I have

190
00:11:42,520 --> 00:11:43,600
two wishes

191
00:11:44,000 --> 00:11:45,720
in this lifetime.

192
00:11:46,920 --> 00:11:47,920
First,

193
00:11:49,160 --> 00:11:53,800
to perform on stage with my senior.

194
00:11:55,960 --> 00:11:57,000
Second,

195
00:12:01,640 --> 00:12:03,360
to find my brother

196
00:12:05,240 --> 00:12:06,960
and tell him

197
00:12:10,120 --> 00:12:11,600
I'm sorry.

198
00:12:15,640 --> 00:12:16,520
Don't worry,

199
00:12:18,200 --> 00:12:19,680
I'll help you find him.

200
00:12:37,960 --> 00:12:40,240
I'm never drinking with you again.

201
00:12:40,880 --> 00:12:42,610
You fall asleep just like that,

202
00:12:42,880 --> 00:12:44,440
like a little pig.

203
00:12:46,520 --> 00:12:48,440
Anyway, what's done is done.

204
00:12:50,360 --> 00:12:51,760
About the veil incident,

205
00:12:52,200 --> 00:12:53,800
don't ever mention it again.

206
00:12:54,160 --> 00:12:55,000
Let's move on.

207
00:12:58,560 --> 00:12:59,400
Good night.

208
00:13:08,040 --> 00:13:09,120
No way.

209
00:13:09,680 --> 00:13:10,480
You

210
00:13:11,040 --> 00:13:13,800
have to agree to one condition.

211
00:13:19,480 --> 00:13:21,640
Will you agree or not?

212
00:13:25,720 --> 00:13:26,760
Yes, I agree.

213
00:13:29,120 --> 00:13:30,680
It's a deal.

214
00:13:52,360 --> 00:13:54,220
Thank you all for your help today.

215
00:13:55,440 --> 00:13:56,800
Take care, Manager Feng.

216
00:13:56,800 --> 00:13:58,660
Give my regards to the old master.

217
00:13:59,760 --> 00:14:01,480
Thank you for your patronage, sir.

218
00:14:01,480 --> 00:14:02,560
Our Mule Society

219
00:14:02,560 --> 00:14:04,220
still relies on your support.

220
00:14:05,080 --> 00:14:05,920
Please stay.

221
00:14:21,120 --> 00:14:22,040
Please wait.

222
00:14:24,040 --> 00:14:25,040
Where is Nanfeng?

223
00:14:25,240 --> 00:14:26,600
Why isn't he here?

224
00:14:27,840 --> 00:14:29,960
He should come greet you.

225
00:14:30,240 --> 00:14:31,800
It's fine, really.

226
00:14:32,160 --> 00:14:34,640
Mr. Lu probably isn't good at socializing.

227
00:14:34,840 --> 00:14:36,000
As a performer...

228
00:14:42,920 --> 00:14:44,360
I came only to perform.

229
00:14:45,120 --> 00:14:46,520
Now that the show is over,

230
00:14:47,080 --> 00:14:49,010
I don't wish to impose any further.

231
00:14:50,280 --> 00:14:51,540
I hope you understand.

232
00:14:57,880 --> 00:14:58,680
Mr. Lu.

233
00:15:01,280 --> 00:15:01,920
Will you

234
00:15:02,280 --> 00:15:03,680
come back again?

235
00:15:05,400 --> 00:15:07,260
If fate allows, we'll meet again.

236
00:15:07,360 --> 00:15:08,680
If you enjoy opera,

237
00:15:08,840 --> 00:15:10,360
you can come to Mule Society.

238
00:15:10,360 --> 00:15:11,890
I'll reserve a seat for you.

239
00:15:15,840 --> 00:15:18,300
If you're concerned about coming as a woman,

240
00:15:18,600 --> 00:15:19,720
you can take this.

241
00:15:20,640 --> 00:15:22,800
Someone will escort you to a private box.

242
00:15:22,800 --> 00:15:24,000
Consider it my thanks

243
00:15:24,400 --> 00:15:25,860
for covering for me today.

244
00:15:36,720 --> 00:15:37,720
Miss.

245
00:15:39,480 --> 00:15:40,480
Miss.

246
00:15:42,000 --> 00:15:43,600
Have you seen the young lady?

247
00:16:04,880 --> 00:16:06,680
It is like leaves in late autumn.

248
00:16:06,920 --> 00:16:08,520
Mountains in the south, waters in the north.

249
00:16:08,520 --> 00:16:09,960
Half a life so lengthy.

250
00:16:10,400 --> 00:16:12,000
Thoughts keep me from sleep.

251
00:16:12,360 --> 00:16:14,200
Thus I write to you.

252
00:16:14,880 --> 00:16:16,560
Thanks to heaven's blessing,

253
00:16:17,280 --> 00:16:19,140
I have had the fortune to meet you.

254
00:16:19,640 --> 00:16:20,360
I, Nanfeng,

255
00:16:20,760 --> 00:16:22,000
am deeply grateful.

256
00:16:23,240 --> 00:16:24,520
You understand music,

257
00:16:25,080 --> 00:16:26,540
harmonize with my melody,

258
00:16:27,080 --> 00:16:28,320
recognize my chimes.

259
00:16:28,400 --> 00:16:30,080
You are the only one who does.

260
00:16:31,680 --> 00:16:34,120
Recently, there are many affairs at Mule Society.

261
00:16:34,120 --> 00:16:36,250
I will handle them as soon as possible,

262
00:16:36,640 --> 00:16:39,040
then express my true feelings.

263
00:16:40,080 --> 00:16:40,840
Miss,

264
00:16:40,840 --> 00:16:41,920
here's freshly made honey pear paste.

265
00:16:41,920 --> 00:16:43,040
It will warm you up.

266
00:16:51,280 --> 00:16:52,600
In my spare time,

267
00:16:53,080 --> 00:16:55,440
I found the opera you performed on stage.

268
00:16:55,920 --> 00:16:57,980
Your voice and image appeared again.

269
00:16:58,640 --> 00:16:59,760
Your voice

270
00:17:00,280 --> 00:17:02,160
is like jade feathers on southern mountains.

271
00:17:02,160 --> 00:17:03,560
Hearing it makes me sing.

272
00:17:04,160 --> 00:17:05,440
The opera says

273
00:17:05,960 --> 00:17:07,240
that longing thoughts

274
00:17:07,440 --> 00:17:09,099
should be kept in moderation.

275
00:17:09,160 --> 00:17:10,920
Yet since first meeting you...

276
00:17:11,839 --> 00:17:13,770
Like an old friend returning home,

277
00:17:14,000 --> 00:17:15,359
I think of you often,

278
00:17:15,359 --> 00:17:16,480
unable to forget.

279
00:17:17,079 --> 00:17:19,440
May the southern wind know my heart,

280
00:17:19,920 --> 00:17:22,200
as I long for my beloved's return.

281
00:17:22,400 --> 00:17:23,800
Thanks to heaven's blessing,

282
00:17:23,800 --> 00:17:25,560
I've had the honor of meeting you.

283
00:17:25,560 --> 00:17:27,960
Nanfeng is deeply grateful and aware.

284
00:17:31,320 --> 00:17:33,050
I can't listen to this anymore.

285
00:17:33,080 --> 00:17:33,920
What else?

286
00:17:34,280 --> 00:17:35,210
Stop reading it.

287
00:17:35,440 --> 00:17:37,640
Finishing it will affect my digestion.

288
00:17:39,520 --> 00:17:40,480
If you ask me,

289
00:17:40,720 --> 00:17:43,050
you should return this letter right away.

290
00:17:43,320 --> 00:17:44,280
I helped you get on stage

291
00:17:44,280 --> 00:17:46,080
because I couldn't stand those stubborn old folks.

292
00:17:46,080 --> 00:17:48,440
But stealing letters is a matter of principle.

293
00:17:48,440 --> 00:17:50,040
If Nanfeng blames someone for this,

294
00:17:50,040 --> 00:17:51,160
I won't speak up for you.

295
00:17:51,160 --> 00:17:52,480
I don't need you to speak for me.

296
00:17:52,480 --> 00:17:54,080
I'll take responsibility for my own actions.

297
00:17:54,080 --> 00:17:55,140
For heaven's sake,

298
00:17:55,480 --> 00:17:56,940
can we stop this nonsense?

299
00:17:57,080 --> 00:17:58,600
A thousand mountains, ten thousand mountains,

300
00:17:58,600 --> 00:17:59,440
no matter how high they stand,

301
00:17:59,440 --> 00:18:01,700
they cannot block the red thread of fate.

302
00:18:02,240 --> 00:18:03,360
My new suit.

303
00:18:03,360 --> 00:18:04,760
Where did you get it from?

304
00:18:04,840 --> 00:18:06,100
I'm not giving it back.

305
00:18:06,920 --> 00:18:08,960
I'll wait until he gets anxious and comes looking for it.

306
00:18:08,960 --> 00:18:10,040
I want to see

307
00:18:10,040 --> 00:18:11,240
who's more important to him -

308
00:18:11,240 --> 00:18:13,040
me or the Xie family's daughter.

309
00:18:19,560 --> 00:18:20,320
Give it to me.

310
00:18:24,520 --> 00:18:25,760
Pay the bill.

311
00:18:25,760 --> 00:18:26,690
It's your treat.

312
00:18:30,680 --> 00:18:31,920
It's completely useless.

313
00:18:31,920 --> 00:18:33,160
And I wanted to treat you to dinner,

314
00:18:33,160 --> 00:18:34,480
go whistle for it.

315
00:18:36,200 --> 00:18:37,000
Watch where you're going!

316
00:18:37,000 --> 00:18:38,320
You blind little girl!

317
00:18:38,440 --> 00:18:39,480
Are you being reasonable?

318
00:18:39,480 --> 00:18:41,610
You're the one who suddenly appeared.

319
00:18:55,760 --> 00:18:56,520
What are you doing?
